      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Pepper and Chorizo Picnic Frittata. The dish belongs to the Italian home-cooking register: straightforward, ingredient-led, calm at the hob. Serves 4.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A weeknight-friendly recipe: most of the work is the prep, and the cooking takes care of itself.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
